{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_02_01_short",
  "title": "奥山すみれ 1話 ドキドキさせてみせます (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私に単独のお仕事が～？\nやったーうれしいっちゃ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A solo job for me?\nYay‚ I’m so chuffed‚ye ken!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "……わー！\n今のナシ！　聞かなかったことにして下さーい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "….Whoa!\nForget I said that. Pretend you never heard me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "奥山さんのその山形弁\n久しぶりに聞いた気がするな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It feels like a long time since I heard\nyour Yamagata dialect.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁっ、恥ずかしいから言わないで下さい\nいつもは、出ないように気を張ってるんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Waah‚ don’t say that. It’s so embarrassing.\nI’m always trying to not let that slip out…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "ほんとーっに時々、つい油断すると\n出ちゃうんですよね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But sometimes I let my guard down‚\nand it just pops out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.166666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "無理に直さなくても。鈴村さんだって\n京都弁のままだし、いいんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t try too hard to fix it. Suzumura-san\nstill speaks Kyoto dialect‚ so isn’t it okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんはおしとやかでプラス補正だからいいんです！\n私のは田舎者っぽいから……マイナス補正なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu-chan is ladylike and classy‚ so it’s fine!\nI’m countrified‚ so it counts against me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.0000001390775,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}